<div>
<p>　　<measure quantity="12" unit="months">
<num value="12">十二</num>月</measure>
<num value="15">戊寅</num>朔<pc>，</pc>複京西錢監<pc>。</pc>己醜<pc>，</pc>置裕民局<pc>。</pc>是歲<pc>，</pc>江<pc>、</pc>淮<pc>、</pc>荊<pc>、</pc>浙<pc>、</pc>
<placeName>梓州</placeName>水<pc>。</pc>出宮女<measure quantity="78" unit="people">
<num value="78">百七十八</num>人</measure>
<pc>。</pc>黃岩民妻<num value="1">一</num>產<num value="4">四</num>男子<pc>。</pc>于闐<pc>、</pc>高麗入貢<pc>。</pc>
